snippet.title: Starship Command for BBC Micro - Longplay - 1227 on 1st command
snippet.description:
Got more than 1000 on first command - then got destroyed at 1313 by a bunch of aliens with plasma torpedoes. 

Played on the b2 emulator (BBC Micro Model B at 130% speed) running on a MacBook Air M1.

Starship Command is a 1983 Acornsoft game for Acorn BBC Model B, written by Peter Irvin. Thank you Peter!
